Problem 2

Here I will create a flexdashboard using plotly for three distinct plot types.

Data

The dataset that I choose to do is “NY Restaurant Inspectations”, which is information on restaurant name and location, type of food, inspection date, and details on violation codes, total scores, and associated grades.

Plotly Boxplot

Using a boxplot to indicate the score distribution in all restaurants in different boroughs.

Plotly Barplot

Using a barplot to indicate the number of top 15 restaurants in Manhattan.

Line Plot
